edu.uga.cs.recdawgs.entity

Interface Student

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable, User

    public interface Student
extends User
    This class represents information about a registered student of in the RecDawgs system. A student is a user who, additionally, has a student id, major, and an address.
